<section class="referral-terms-section">
  <div class="page-width page-width--narrow">
    <div class="referral-terms__intro">
      <p class="referral-terms__eyebrow">Fine Print</p>
      <h1 class="referral-terms__heading">Referral Program Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
      <p class="referral-terms__effective">Effective 2026-04-12</p>
    </div>

    <div class="referral-terms__body">
      <h2>Plain-language summary</h2>
      <p>Refer someone to The Sole Provider. When their first invoice is paid, you earn store credit on your account. Existing clients earn 4% store credit; non-clients earn 2% store credit (redeemable when you place your own order). The person you refer gets 5% off their first order. That's the whole deal. The fine print is below.</p>

      <h2>Eligibility</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Anyone can make a referral — current clients, former clients, friends of clients, or members of the public.</li>
        <li>The person being referred must be a <strong>new customer</strong> who has not previously ordered from The Sole Provider.</li>
        <li>Self-referrals are not eligible. You cannot refer your own business, a business you own or operate, or an account you control.</li>
        <li>The referred customer must mention the referrer's name when requesting a quote or placing their first order. Retroactive credit is not available.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Reward Rates</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Existing clients:</strong> 4% of the referred customer's first paid invoice, issued as store credit.</li>
        <li><strong>Non-client referrers:</strong> 2% of the referred customer's first paid invoice, issued as store credit. Non-client credit becomes usable when the referrer places their own order with The Sole Provider.</li>
        <li><strong>New-customer discount:</strong> The referred customer receives 5% off their first order as a thank-you for joining us.</li>
        <li>Reward percentages apply to the item total of the referred order, not to taxes, shipping fees, or setup/art fees.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How Rewards Are Issued</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>All referral rewards are issued as <strong>store credit</strong>. Cash payouts are not available.</li>
        <li>Credit is added to the referrer's account automatically when the referred customer's invoice is marked paid in full.</li>
        <li>Store credit <strong>never expires</strong>. Once earned, it is the client's to use on any future order.</li>
        <li>There is no limit on the number of referrals a person can make in any given period.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Voided or Refunded Orders</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>If a referred customer's order is voided, cancelled, or fully refunded before production, the referral reward is forfeited and any associated credit will be reversed.</li>
        <li>Partial refunds do not typically affect referral rewards, but The Sole Provider reserves the right to adjust rewards pro-rata in cases of substantial partial refunds.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Using Your Store Credit</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Store credit can be applied to any invoice, in full or in part, at the time of quote or order.</li>
        <li>Credit can be combined with account credits from other sources (loyalty, manual grants, etc.) on the same order.</li>
        <li>Credit cannot be transferred, sold, or assigned to another person or account.</li>
        <li>Credit has no cash value and cannot be redeemed for cash.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Program Changes</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>The Sole Provider reserves the right to modify, suspend, or discontinue the referral program at any time, with or without notice.</li>
        <li>Reward rates are subject to change. Any changes apply only to new referrals made after the effective date of the change; previously earned credit is not affected.</li>
        <li>The Sole Provider reserves the right to disqualify any referral that appears to be fraudulent, manipulative, or made in bad faith.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Questions</h2>
      <p>Contact Sean at <a href="mailto:solepdistributions@gmail.com">solepdistributions@gmail.com</a> for any questions about the referral program or your earned credit.</p>

      <div class="referral-terms__cta-wrap">
        <a href="/pages/referral-program" class="referral-terms__back">&lsaquo; Back to the referral program</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

